public enum ResourceType
extends Enum<ResourceType>

ResourceType states the possible BELFramework cache sub-directories that correspond to BELFramework resources.

Author:
Anthony Bargnesi <abargnesi@selventa.com>

fromLocation

public static ResourceType fromLocation(String resourceLocation)
Returns the ResourceType inferred from the resource location.

The resource location must end with the resourceExtension or the resourceExtension + .

Parameters:
resourceLocation - String, the resource location
Returns:
ResourceType the resource type inferred from the resource location. A null will be returned if there was no match or if the resourceLocation argument was null
